{"id":165488,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2011/07/思科为重庆提供网络监控设备/","date":"2011-07-05T20:54:29Z","modified":"2012-07-02T07:32:33Z","title":"思科为重庆提供网络监控设备","content":"<p>《华尔街日报》报导，包括思科在内的西方企业正准备帮助重庆新建一个雄心勃勃的监控项目──在全城范围内安装多达50万个摄像头的监控网络，政府官员们说这一网络能起到防止犯罪的作用，而人权倡导者则警告说，该监控网有可能针对持不同政见者。这个被称作“平安重庆”的监控网按计划将覆盖1,000多平方公里范围内的50万个十字路口、居民社区和公园，其覆盖范围比纽约市还大25%以上。思科预计会向该项目提供网络设备，海康威视是主承包商。思科发言人表示该公司遵守美国的出口限制法律，不会出口用于镇压的设备。<img width=\"1\" height=\"1\" src=\"http://solidot.org.feedsportal.com/c/33236/f/556826/s/166d990d/mf.gif\" border=\"0\" /></p>\n<div>\n<table border=\"0\">\n<tr>\n<td valign=\"middle\"><a href=\"http://res.feedsportal.com/viral/sendemail2.html?title=%E6%80%9D%E7%A7%91%E4%B8%BA%E9%87%8D%E5%BA%86%E6%8F%90%E4%BE%9B%E7%BD%91%E7%BB%9C%E7%9B%91%E6%8E%A7%E8%AE%BE%E5%A4%87&#038;link=http%3A%2F%2Fit.solidot.org%2Farticle.pl%3Fsid%3D11%2F07%2F05%2F0845226%26amp%3Bfrom%3Drss\"><img src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/images/emailthis2.gif\" border=\"0\" /></a></td>\n<td valign=\"middle\"><a href=\"http://res.feedsportal.com/viral/bookmark.cfm?title=%E6%80%9D%E7%A7%91%E4%B8%BA%E9%87%8D%E5%BA%86%E6%8F%90%E4%BE%9B%E7%BD%91%E7%BB%9C%E7%9B%91%E6%8E%A7%E8%AE%BE%E5%A4%87&#038;link=http%3A%2F%2Fit.solidot.org%2Farticle.pl%3Fsid%3D11%2F07%2F05%2F0845226%26amp%3Bfrom%3Drss\"><img src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/images/bookmark.gif\" border=\"0\" /></a></td>\n</tr>\n</table>\n</div>\n<p><a href=\"http://da.feedsportal.com/r/106216523291/u/49/f/556826/c/33236/s/166d990d/a2.htm\"><img src=\"http://da.feedsportal.com/r/106216523291/u/49/f/556826/c/33236/s/166d990d/a2.img\" border=\"0\" /></a></p>\n<div>\n<a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/solidot?a=51foPDYONh4:jiJk4Tz6wfA:yIl2AUoC8zA\"><img src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/solidot?d=yIl2AUoC8zA\" border=\"0\" /></a> <a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/solidot?a=51foPDYONh4:jiJk4Tz6wfA:7Q72WNTAKBA\"><img src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/solidot?d=7Q72WNTAKBA\" border=\"0\" /></a>\n</div>\n</p>\n<p>